  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2630020/extras/a1d5c5aad154c901b2c9470834cd7d20.avif?t=1772417972\" width=780 height=78 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The young girl Rayne, who became the sacred knight of the kingdom, was entrusted by Jas, the leader of the sacred knights and her lover, to investigate the disturbances occurring in a distant town named \"Hakudeti\".  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >These disturbances involved a surge in criminals in the previously peaceful town of Hakudeti, an overflow of monsters in the nearby areas, and even the appearance of a mysterious dungeon.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2630020/extras/d3049d0ceeb7e3217906a82c6ac21e84.avif?t=1772417972\" width=780 height=78 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Players will control the protagonist, Rayne, and experience her adventure. Delve into mysterious dungeons, vanquish monsters, and investigate the disturbances, all while trying to restore peace to the kingdom!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2630020/extras/eb6289af7d0029036c1dd53306f0ec28.avif?t=1772417972\" width=780 height=77 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >JRPG</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Turn-based command combat</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Female protagonist</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2630020/extras/a1d5c5aad154c901b2c9470834cd7d20.avif?t=1772417972\" width=780 height=78 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The young girl Rayne, who became the sacred knight of the kingdom, was entrusted by Jas, the leader of the sacred knights and her lover, to investigate the disturbances occurring in a distant town named \"Hakudeti\".  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >These disturbances involved a surge in criminals in the previously peaceful town of Hakudeti, an overflow of monsters in the nearby areas, and even the appearance of a mysterious dungeon.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2630020/extras/d3049d0ceeb7e3217906a82c6ac21e84.avif?t=1772417972\" width=780 height=78 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Players will control the protagonist, Rayne, and experience her adventure. Delve into mysterious dungeons, vanquish monsters, and investigate the disturbances, all while trying to restore peace to the kingdom!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2630020/extras/eb6289af7d0029036c1dd53306f0ec28.avif?t=1772417972\" width=780 height=77 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >JRPG</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Turn-based command combat</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Female protagonist</p></li></ul>",
